commit.title: Propagating scope information in indirect application to a reference.
commit.message:
Propagating scope information in indirect application to a reference.

This allows the following to interpret "0" in the expected scope:

Notation "0" := true : bool_scope.
Axiom f : bool -> bool -> nat.
Record R := { p : bool -> nat }.
Check (@f 0) 0.
Check fun r => r.(@p) 0.
